header(class="sticky top-0 z-20 border-b border-zinc-200 bg-white/95 backdrop-blur dark:border-zinc-800 dark:bg-zinc-950/95")
    div(class="flex flex-col gap-3 px-5 py-4 md:flex-row md:items-center md:justify-between")
        div
            div(class="flex items-center gap-2 text-xs font-medium text-zinc-500 dark:text-zinc-400")
                i(class="fa-solid fa-gear")
                span System
            h1(class="mt-1 text-xl font-semibold text-zinc-950 dark:text-zinc-50") 시스템 설정
        button(type="button", (click)="load()", class="inline-flex h-9 items-center gap-2 rounded-md border border-zinc-300 bg-white px-3 text-sm font-semibold text-zinc-700 hover:bg-zinc-50 dark:border-zinc-700 dark:bg-zinc-900 dark:text-zinc-200 dark:hover:bg-zinc-800")
            i(class="fa-solid fa-rotate-right")
            span 새로고침

main(class="space-y-5 px-5 py-5")
    div(*ngIf="loading()", class="h-32 rounded-md border border-zinc-200 bg-white p-5 text-sm text-zinc-500 dark:border-zinc-800 dark:bg-zinc-900 dark:text-zinc-400") 정보를 불러오는 중입니다.
    div(*ngIf="error()", class="rounded-md border border-rose-200 bg-rose-50 px-4 py-3 text-sm text-rose-700 dark:border-rose-900/70 dark:bg-rose-950/40 dark:text-rose-300") {{error()}}

    div(*ngIf="!loading() && !error()", class="space-y-5")
        section(class="grid grid-cols-1 gap-5 xl:grid-cols-[460px_1fr]")
            div(class="rounded-md border border-zinc-200 bg-white dark:border-zinc-800 dark:bg-zinc-900")
                div(class="border-b border-zinc-200 px-4 py-3 dark:border-zinc-800")
                    h2(class="text-sm font-semibold text-zinc-950 dark:text-zinc-50") General
                    p(class="mt-1 text-xs text-zinc-500 dark:text-zinc-400") 브라우저 제목, favicon, 사이드바 로고를 저장 시 한 번에 적용합니다.
                div(class="space-y-4 p-4")
                    label(class="block")
                        span(class="mb-1 block text-xs font-semibold text-zinc-500 dark:text-zinc-400") 브라우저 제목
                        input(type="text", data-testid="system-browser-title", [(ngModel)]="general.browser_title", class="h-10 w-full rounded-md border border-zinc-300 bg-white px-3 text-sm text-zinc-900 focus:border-zinc-500 focus:outline-none focus:ring-1 focus:ring-zinc-500 dark:border-zinc-700 dark:bg-zinc-950 dark:text-zinc-100")

                    div(class="grid grid-cols-1 gap-4 md:grid-cols-2")
                        div(class="rounded-md border border-zinc-200 p-4 dark:border-zinc-800")
                            div(class="flex items-start justify-between gap-3")
                                div
                                    p(class="text-sm font-semibold text-zinc-950 dark:text-zinc-50") Favicon
                                    p(class="mt-1 text-xs text-zinc-500 dark:text-zinc-400") SVG, PNG, ICO를 지원합니다.
                                div(class="flex h-12 w-12 items-center justify-center rounded-md border border-zinc-200 bg-zinc-50 dark:border-zinc-700 dark:bg-zinc-950")
                                    img([src]="previewUrl('favicon')", alt="favicon", class="h-8 w-8 rounded object-contain")
                            input(id="system-favicon-upload", type="file", accept=".ico,.png,.svg,.gif,.jpg,.jpeg,.webp", class="hidden", (change)="selectAsset('favicon', $event)")
                            div(class="mt-3 flex flex-wrap items-center gap-2")
                                button(type="button", (click)="openAssetPicker('system-favicon-upload')", class="inline-flex h-9 items-center gap-2 rounded-md border border-zinc-300 px-3 text-sm font-semibold text-zinc-700 hover:bg-zinc-50 dark:border-zinc-700 dark:text-zinc-200 dark:hover:bg-zinc-800")
                                    i(class="fa-solid fa-image")
                                    span 이미지 선택
                                button(*ngIf="hasPendingAsset('favicon')", type="button", (click)="clearSelectedAsset('favicon')", class="inline-flex h-9 items-center gap-2 rounded-md border border-rose-300 px-3 text-sm font-semibold text-rose-700 hover:bg-rose-50 dark:border-rose-900/70 dark:text-rose-300 dark:hover:bg-rose-950/30")
                                    i(class="fa-solid fa-xmark")
                                    span 선택 취소
                            p(class="mt-2 text-xs text-zinc-500 dark:text-zinc-400")
                                span(*ngIf="hasPendingAsset('favicon')") {{pendingAssetName('favicon')}} 파일을 선택했습니다. 저장 시 업로드됩니다.
                                span(*ngIf="!hasPendingAsset('favicon')") Favicon 경로는 고정되어 있으며 새 이미지를 저장하면 기존 파일을 대체합니다.
                        div(class="rounded-md border border-zinc-200 p-4 dark:border-zinc-800")
                            div(class="flex items-start justify-between gap-3")
                                div
                                    p(class="text-sm font-semibold text-zinc-950 dark:text-zinc-50") Sidebar Logo
                                    p(class="mt-1 text-xs text-zinc-500 dark:text-zinc-400") 좌측 메뉴 상단에 표시되는 브랜드 이미지
                                div(class="flex h-12 w-12 items-center justify-center overflow-hidden rounded-md border border-zinc-200 bg-zinc-50 dark:border-zinc-700 dark:bg-zinc-950")
                                    img(*ngIf="previewUrl('logo')", [src]="previewUrl('logo')", alt="logo", class="h-full w-full object-contain")
                                    span(*ngIf="!previewUrl('logo')", class="text-xs font-semibold text-zinc-400") 없음
                            input(id="system-logo-upload", type="file", accept=".png,.svg,.gif,.jpg,.jpeg,.webp", class="hidden", (change)="selectAsset('logo', $event)")
                            div(class="mt-3 flex flex-wrap items-center gap-2")
                                button(type="button", (click)="openAssetPicker('system-logo-upload')", class="inline-flex h-9 items-center gap-2 rounded-md border border-zinc-300 px-3 text-sm font-semibold text-zinc-700 hover:bg-zinc-50 dark:border-zinc-700 dark:text-zinc-200 dark:hover:bg-zinc-800")
                                    i(class="fa-solid fa-image")
                                    span 이미지 선택
                                button(*ngIf="hasPendingAsset('logo')", type="button", (click)="clearSelectedAsset('logo')", class="inline-flex h-9 items-center gap-2 rounded-md border border-rose-300 px-3 text-sm font-semibold text-rose-700 hover:bg-rose-50 dark:border-rose-900/70 dark:text-rose-300 dark:hover:bg-rose-950/30")
                                    i(class="fa-solid fa-xmark")
                                    span 선택 취소
                            p(class="mt-2 text-xs text-zinc-500 dark:text-zinc-400")
                                span(*ngIf="hasPendingAsset('logo')") {{pendingAssetName('logo')}} 파일을 선택했습니다. 저장 시 업로드됩니다.
                                span(*ngIf="!hasPendingAsset('logo')") Logo 경로는 고정되어 있으며 새 이미지를 저장하면 기존 파일을 대체합니다.

                    button(type="button", data-testid="system-general-save", (click)="saveGeneral()", [disabled]="savingGeneral()", class="inline-flex h-10 w-full items-center justify-center gap-2 rounded-md bg-zinc-950 px-3 text-sm font-semibold text-white hover:bg-zinc-800 disabled:opacity-60 dark:bg-zinc-100 dark:text-zinc-950 dark:hover:bg-zinc-200")
                        i(class="fa-solid fa-floppy-disk")
                        span {{savingGeneral() ? '저장 중...' : '일반 설정 저장'}}

            div(class="rounded-md border border-zinc-200 bg-white dark:border-zinc-800 dark:bg-zinc-900")
                div(class="flex items-start justify-between gap-3 border-b border-zinc-200 px-4 py-3 dark:border-zinc-800")
                    div
                        h2(class="text-sm font-semibold text-zinc-950 dark:text-zinc-50") 서비스 백업 시스템
                        p(class="mt-1 text-xs text-zinc-500 dark:text-zinc-400") 외부 Harbor 계정은 사용하지 않고 이 장비에 로컬 Harbor를 띄워 서비스 이미지 백업에만 사용합니다.
                    span(class="inline-flex rounded-md border px-2 py-1 text-xs font-semibold", [ngClass]="backupSystem.status === 'running' ? 'border-emerald-200 bg-emerald-50 text-emerald-700 dark:border-emerald-900/70 dark:bg-emerald-950/40 dark:text-emerald-300' : backupSystem.status === 'failed' ? 'border-rose-200 bg-rose-50 text-rose-700 dark:border-rose-900/70 dark:bg-rose-950/40 dark:text-rose-300' : 'border-zinc-200 bg-zinc-50 text-zinc-600 dark:border-zinc-700 dark:bg-zinc-950 dark:text-zinc-300'") {{backupStatusLabel()}}
                div(class="space-y-4 p-4")
                    div(class="grid grid-cols-1 gap-3 md:grid-cols-2")
                        div(class="rounded-md border border-zinc-200 px-3 py-3 dark:border-zinc-800")
                            p(class="text-xs font-semibold text-zinc-500 dark:text-zinc-400") Harbor URL
                            p(class="mt-2 truncate text-sm font-semibold text-zinc-950 dark:text-zinc-50") {{backupSystem.harbor_url || '-'}}
                        div(class="rounded-md border border-zinc-200 px-3 py-3 dark:border-zinc-800")
                            p(class="text-xs font-semibold text-zinc-500 dark:text-zinc-400") 관리자 계정
                            p(class="mt-2 text-sm font-semibold text-zinc-950 dark:text-zinc-50") {{backupSystem.admin_username || 'admin'}}
                        div(class="rounded-md border border-zinc-200 px-3 py-3 dark:border-zinc-800 md:col-span-2")
                            p(class="text-xs font-semibold text-zinc-500 dark:text-zinc-400") 저장 경로
                            p(class="mt-2 break-all text-sm font-semibold text-zinc-950 dark:text-zinc-50") {{backupSystem.data_path || '-'}}
                        div(class="rounded-md border border-zinc-200 px-3 py-3 dark:border-zinc-800")
                            p(class="text-xs font-semibold text-zinc-500 dark:text-zinc-400") 남은 용량
                            p(class="mt-2 text-sm font-semibold text-zinc-950 dark:text-zinc-50") {{formatBytes(backupSystem.storage?.available_bytes)}} / {{formatBytes(backupSystem.storage?.total_bytes)}}
                        div(class="rounded-md border border-zinc-200 px-3 py-3 dark:border-zinc-800")
                            p(class="text-xs font-semibold text-zinc-500 dark:text-zinc-400") 설치 상태
                            p(class="mt-2 text-sm font-semibold text-zinc-950 dark:text-zinc-50") {{backupSystem.installed ? '설치됨' : '설치 필요'}}
                    div(*ngIf="backupSystem.last_error", class="rounded-md border border-rose-200 bg-rose-50 px-3 py-2 text-sm text-rose-700 dark:border-rose-900/70 dark:bg-rose-950/40 dark:text-rose-300") {{backupSystem.last_error}}
                    div(class="flex flex-wrap items-center gap-2")
                        button(type="button", (click)="runBackupAction('start')", [disabled]="backupBusy() || backupSystem.status === 'running'", class="inline-flex h-10 items-center gap-2 rounded-md bg-zinc-950 px-3 text-sm font-semibold text-white hover:bg-zinc-800 disabled:opacity-60 dark:bg-zinc-100 dark:text-zinc-950 dark:hover:bg-zinc-200")
                            i(class="fa-solid fa-play")
                            span {{backupSystem.installed ? '시작' : '설치 후 시작'}}
                        button(type="button", (click)="runBackupAction('restart')", [disabled]="backupBusy() || !backupSystem.installed", class="inline-flex h-10 items-center gap-2 rounded-md border border-zinc-300 px-3 text-sm font-semibold text-zinc-700 hover:bg-zinc-50 disabled:opacity-60 dark:border-zinc-700 dark:text-zinc-200 dark:hover:bg-zinc-800")
                            i(class="fa-solid fa-rotate")
                            span 재시작
                        button(type="button", (click)="runBackupAction('stop')", [disabled]="backupBusy() || !backupSystem.installed || backupSystem.status !== 'running'", class="inline-flex h-10 items-center gap-2 rounded-md border border-rose-300 px-3 text-sm font-semibold text-rose-700 hover:bg-rose-50 disabled:opacity-60 dark:border-rose-900/70 dark:text-rose-300 dark:hover:bg-rose-950/30")
                            i(class="fa-solid fa-stop")
                            span 정지
                        button(type="button", (click)="refreshBackupSystem()", [disabled]="backupBusy()", class="inline-flex h-10 items-center gap-2 rounded-md border border-zinc-300 px-3 text-sm font-semibold text-zinc-700 hover:bg-zinc-50 disabled:opacity-60 dark:border-zinc-700 dark:text-zinc-200 dark:hover:bg-zinc-800")
                            i(class="fa-solid", [ngClass]="backupBusy() ? 'fa-spinner fa-spin' : 'fa-rotate-right'")
                            span 상태 갱신
